The Third View(3)
.
.
Last, be happy of what you get! Some of us end up being blind, hungry, poor,  exhausted, ect. Not being so lucky in life. The most important thing is not to complained about it but to make the most of it. Knowing your incapability and see your potential and then own it!
.
.
#streetphotography
#sonynex6 #50mm
#jogjakartaistimewa
#loveindonesia #indonesiaforever

The Third View(2)
.
.
Second, facial expressions is the best way to communicate. You may knew nothing about the person you just met. But, their facial expressions tells a story. What they have been through this morning, he or she doesn't have anything to eat yesterday,  being very lucky today, or someone important just died about a week ago. Happiness and sadness its just a small part of feelings, the rest part is written on their faces. .
.
#streetphotography
#sonynex6 #50mm
#jogjakartaistimewa
#loveindonesia 
#indonesiaforever

The Third View (1)
.
The street thought me 3 things in this past week. .
.
First, there's no such thing as a stranger.  Because everybody is somebody for the person sitting next to him or her. Neglecting every differences between one person from the other, makes a friend. Knowing them to the root makes a family.
.
.
